<h1>Improve Your Life</h1>
<p><strong><font color="red">BULLETIN.</font></strong> It's time for SWIMMING LESSONS!  Private lessons start immediately and group lessons begin June 2nd.  <a href="http://www.cordovaathleticclub.com/swimming.pdf">Click here</a> for the June group classes.  Stop by or call (901) 752-1111 and ask for Jason to schedule a private lesson.</p>
<p><strong>Our Club.</strong> Cordova Athletic Club strives to meet all of your fitness needs as well as offer the finest service and amenities available. Unlike any other club in the area, Cordova Athletic Club offers a unique balance of fitness and programs for the entire family.  From our state-of-the-art fitness equipment to over 60 group exercise classes per week,  Cordova Athletic Club covers every aspect of becoming or staying active.</p>
<p><strong>Our Staff.</strong> Our professional staff is constantly working to create a comfortable, service driven atmosphere for members of all ages and fitness levels. A full-time maintenance staff maintains immaculate conditions throughout the club. </p>
